'''昔加末县'''（{{lang-ms|Daerah Segamat}}），是[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]][[柔佛州|柔佛州]]最北部的一个县，其面积为2,807.29平方公里<ref name=":2">{{cite web|url=https://ptj.johor.gov.my/index.php/pejabat-tanah/pejabat-tanah-segamat/profil-daerah|title=Profil Daerah Segamat|accessdate=2018-11-09|author=|date=|work=Laman Rasmi Pentadbiran Tanah Johor|publisher=Pejabat Tanah Segamat|language=ms|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180928202240/https://ptj.johor.gov.my/index.php/pejabat-tanah/pejabat-tanah-segamat/profil-daerah|archive-date=2018-09-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2010年总人口为189,820<ref name=":Demo2010">{{Cite book|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150301154300/http://www.statistics.gov.my/portal/download_Population/files/census2010/Taburan_Penduduk_dan_Ciri-ciri_Asas_Demografi.pdf|title=Taburan Penduduk dan Ciri-ciri Asas Demografi 2010 (PDF)|last=|first=|publisher=Jabatan Perangkaan Malaysia|year=2011|isbn=978-983-9044-54-6|location=Putrajaya|pages=|access-date=2018-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230115455/https://web.archive.org/web/20150301154300/http://www.statistics.gov.my/portal/download_Population/files/census2010/Taburan_Penduduk_dan_Ciri-ciri_Asas_Demografi.pdf|archive-date=2018-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。昔加末县除了县府[[昔加末|昔加末市]]外，还有[[拉美士|拉美士]]、[[利民达|利民达]]、{{le|巫罗加什|Buloh Kasap}}、[[峇都安南|峇都安南]]、[[三合港|三合港]]、[[彼咯|彼咯]]、{{le|双溪加叻|Sungai Karas}}、{{le|丁能|Tenang}}和{{le|金馬士峇魯|Gemas Baharu}}等市镇。

== 行政区划 ==
昔加末县下辖11个[[巫金|巫金]]（区）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mygeoportal.gov.my/sites/default/files/UPI/KOD%20DAN%20NAMA%20SEMPADAN%20PENTADBIRAN%20TANAH_JOHOR.pdf|title=Kod dan Nama Sempadan Pentadbiran Tanah, Unique Parcel Identifier (UPI) JOHOR|accessdate=|author=|date=2011|publisher=Jawatankuasa Teknikal Standard MyGDI (JTSM)|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181124045351/http://www.mygeoportal.gov.my/sites/default/files/UPI/KOD%20DAN%20NAMA%20SEMPADAN%20PENTADBIRAN%20TANAH_JOHOR.pdf|archive-date=2018-11-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://apps.water.gov.my/jpskomuniti/dokumen/Segamat%20Profil%20(LATEST).pdf|title=Profil Daerah Segamat|accessdate=|author=|date=|publisher=Jabatan Pengairan dan Saliran Daerah Segamat|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818020810/http://apps.water.gov.my/jpskomuniti/dokumen/Segamat%20Profil%20(LATEST).pdf|archive-date=2016-08-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
