==教育==
{{GeoGroup}}
昔加末县内目前共有20间华文小学<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://web.jiaozong.org.my/doc/srjk/johor-srjk.pdf|title=柔佛华小通讯录|accessdate=2018-10-25|author=|date=2017-01|publisher=马来西亚华校教师会总会（教总）|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180304152301/http://web.jiaozong.org.my/doc/srjk/johor-srjk.pdf|archive-date=2018-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.sinchew.com.my/node/1064953|title=昔县华小生逐年减．10年了少2222人|date=2016-01-06|newspaper=星洲网 Sin Chew Daily|accessdate=2018-10-31|language=zh-hans|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181031133115/http://www.sinchew.com.my/node/1064953|archive-date=2018-10-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及一间[[马来西亚国民型华文中学|国民型华文中学]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.dongzong.my/resource/images/doc/SMJK/smjk_contact.pdf|title=国民型中学通讯录|accessdate=2018-10-26|author=|date=2009-06|publisher=马来西亚华校教师会总会（教总）|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181026025122/https://www.dongzong.my/resource/images/doc/SMJK/smjk_contact.pdf|archive-date=2018-10-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

